OL,6,FStarmer said the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FLegacy Act "was unfit not least
OL,8,Fbecause it gave immunity to hundreds
OL,9,Fof terrorists and wasn't supported by
OL,10,Fvictims in Northern Ireland nor I
OL,11,Fbelieve by any of the political
OL,12,Fparties in Northern Ireland".
OL,14,F"The court found it unlawful. We will
OL,15,Fput in place a better framework, we're
OL,16,Fworking on a draft remedial order and
OL,17,Freplacement legislation, and we will
OL,18,Flook at every conceivable way to
OL,19,Fprevent these types of cases claiming
OL,20,Fdamages," he added.
