OL,6,FThe relevant sections of the Legacy
OL,7,FAct had been agreed by Parliament in
OL,8,F2023 in response to a Supreme Court
OL,9,Fjudgment in 2020 that paved the way
OL,10,Ffor former Sinn Fein leader Mr Adams
OL,11,Fto secure compensation over his
OL,12,Finternment without trial in the early
OL,13,F1970s.
OL,15,FMr Adams won his appeal to overturn
OL,16,Fhistorical convictions for two
OL,17,Fattempted prison breaks, after he was
OL,18,Finterned without trial in 1973 at Long
OL,19,FKesh internment camp, also known as
OL,20,FMaze Prison, near Lisburn.
