OL,6,FHowever, in February last year, the
OL,7,FHigh Court in Belfast ruled that the
OL,8,Fprovisions of the Act related to the
OL,9,FICOs were incompatible with the
OL,10,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights.
OL,12,FThe current government has not
OL,13,Fappealed that judgment and has tabled
OL,14,Fa remedial order in Parliament that
OL,15,Fwill repeal various parts of the
OL,16,FLegacy Act, including the sections on
OL,17,FICOs.
